    {
      "sort": 200000,
      "name": "Automate and Fumble XP (GM only)",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "WyR6m6LOKiF3HVmB",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>There are two checkboxes.</p><p><strong>Automate XP</strong></p><p>If this option is turned on then any skill, trait or passion will get an XP check added whenever a Critical, Success or Fumble is rolled.</p><p>Traits that are fumbled award the XP check to the opposing trait.</p><p>When using a weapon the XP check is applied to the relevant skill.</p><p>You can still manually check and uncheck the XP boxes on individual skills etc.</p><p>An Inquiry Roll, Dodge or Evade combat action will not automatically add an XP check.</p><p></p><p><strong>Fumble XP</strong></p><p>If turned off then Automate XP All will not be granted in the event of a Fumble. If Automate XP All is turned off then this will have no effect.</p><p></p><table><tbody><tr><td><p></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Automate XP On</strong></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Automate XP Off</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Fumble XP On</strong></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align:center\">XP checks added automatically for Critical, Success &amp; Fumble</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align:center\">Add XP checks manually</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Fumble XP Off</strong></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align:center\">XP checks added automatically for Critical  &amp; Success</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align:center\">Add XP checks manually</p></td></tr></tbody></table>"
      },
      "video": {
        "controls": true,
        "volume": 0.5
      },
      "src": null,
